<hr>
<p><font size=2><strong>December 15, 1995</strong></font></p>
<p align=center>The last NEWSLETTER of the year 1995 has now reached you, together with the 
Appendix of the Annual Report on the activities of the Centre in English, and we hope that it 
will keep us all in touch and give ideas for future cooperation. We, editors of this 
Newsletter, Inguna Bekere and Gunilla Fors&eacute;n, are glad for positive response to our 
Newsletter. If there are institutions etc. who do not receive it please let us know and we will 
put you on our mailing list. We hope to be able to produce four issues next years. We thank 
you all for good collaboration and wish you<br>
A MERRY CHRISTMAS <br>
and A FRUITFUL NEW YEAR!<br>
Inguna Bekere and Gunilla Fors&eacute;n</p>
<hr>
