<h2>Inauguration of the Centre 26 september</h2>
<p><img src="images/PeterCurmanToastmaster.JPG" align=left hspace=10 width=250 height=189><strong>Peter Curman</strong>, Sweden, was the 
toastmaster for the night. Among others 
he presented following speakers:</p>
<p><a href="960926-5.htm"><strong>Jan Lundgren</strong></a>, Mayor of Visby, 
Gotland, Sweden<br>
<a href="960926-6.htm"><strong>Lars-Erik Blomqvist</strong></a>, chairman of the 
Swedish Writers' Union<br>
<a href="960926-7.htm"><strong>Gunilla Fors&eacute;n</strong></a>, Director of the Baltic 
Writers' and Translators' Centre<br clear=all>
</p>
