<title>Seminar on literture and internet - 23 september 1996</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
<meta name="FORMATTER" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<p align="center"><font size="7">Internet and Literature</font><br>
<font size="5">News from the seminar 23 september 1996</font></p>
<hr>
<div align="left">
<table cellpadding="5" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td colspan="2" width="66%"><font size="6">Writers and
        translators from 40 countries<br>
        </font>I<font size="4">n the Congress Hall of Paradise
        Hotel at Rhodes writers and translators gathered to
        discuss Internet and Literature.</font>
        <p><img src="sea.jpg" align="bottom" width="350"
        height="162"> </p>
        <p><em><strong>This is a continously updated report from
        the seminar at Paradise Hotel, at the blue Meditiranean
        Sea on Rhodes Greece.</strong></em> </p>
        </td>
        <td valign="top" width="34%">
        <h3>Content </h3>
        <p><strong>Opening of the conference<br>
        </strong><a href="01.htm"><strong>Session 1</strong></a> </p>
        <p><strong>Internet as a tool for freedom of expression
        in easten Europe and Balkan<br>
        </strong><a href="02.htm"><strong>Session 2</strong></a> </p>
        <p><strong>Who i responsible for the information? What
        about safety on the net?<br>
        </strong><a href="03.htm"><strong>Session 3</strong></a> </p>
        <p><strong>Copyright issues, creativity and freedom of
        expression<br>
        </strong><a href="04.htm"><strong>Session 4</strong></a><strong> </strong></p>
        <p><strong>A strong link between copyright and freedom of
        expression<br>
        </strong><a href="05.htm"><strong>Session 5</strong></a> </p>
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td valign="top" width="33%"><a
        href="02.htm#Internetional"><font size="5">InterNETional</font></a><br>
        <font size="4">- a coming online internet magazine</font><br>
        Novica Milic from the Belgrad Circle presented his plans
        for a new magazine InterNETional. The aim with this
        project is to promote &#147;internetional&#148; contacts;
        to create new kinds of virtual communities.</td>
        <td valign="top" width="33%"><font size="4">Evening
        programme:</font><br>
        <a href="poetry.htm"><font size="6">Poetry reading</font></a><br>
        in the Sun Wing Hotel Amfi Theatre
        <p><a href="06.htm"><font size="5"><strong>Hands-on
        Internet</strong></font></a><br>
        On wednesday the participants got oportunity to train in
        the use of Internet</p>
        </td>
        <td valign="top" width="34%"><a href="particip.htm"><font
        size="5">Participants</font></a><font size="5"> of the
        inauguration</font>
        <hr>
        <p><font size="6">We thank all our </font><a
        href="http://www.marebalticum.se/rhodes/sponsors.htm"><font
        size="6">sponsors</font></a></p>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
</div>
