<h1>Poetry reading in the mediteranian night</h1>
<p><img src="images/poetry.JPG" align="bottom" width="300"
height="181"></p>
<h4>Over 100 participants were listening for the poetry presented
by the poets and translators from as far as Norway, Ireland,
Romania and Vietnam among much more countries. The reading took
place in Sun Wing Hotel Amfi Theatre close to the sound of the
waves of the Mediteranian sea.</h4>
<p><strong>Let us present one of the performers </strong><a
href="poetry-ileana.htm"><font size="4"><strong>Ileana Malancioiu</strong></font></a><strong>,
from Romania.</strong></p>
