<DOCHDR>
http://www.marebalticum.se:80/rhodes/poetry-ileana.htm 194.198.228.141 19970124042953 text/html 4825
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Microsoft-IIS/2.0
Date: Fri, 24 Jan 1997 04:40:28 GMT
Content-Type: text/html
