<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE> george jr. / february 1997 / arcadia</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#336699" VLINK="#c0c0c0" ALINK="#c0c0c0">
<IMG SRC="/graphics/arcadiab.gif" WIDTH=402 HEIGHT=34 ALIGN=left>
<BR CLEAR=ALL>
<HR>
<P>
<table cellpadding=10>

<tr><td>

<P>

<h2><A HREF="federman.html">the uneasy chair</A></h2>

<!--text here-->
The esteemed writer Raymond Federman - novelist, translator, literary pioneer - says the whole shebang has gone to heck in a handbag. And what are we going to do about it?
<br clear=all>
<P>

<H2><A HREF="monkey/monkey.html">monkey buttons</a></H2>
<IMG SRC="monkman.gif" WIDTH=45 HEIGHT=70 ALIGN=left border=1>
<!--text here-->
Well, the problem has been put; but will
                       monkey buttons solve a thing? Heck
                       no. (That's two hecks, and you're
                       counting.) This wee diversion will send
                       you on a scavenger hunt inside
                       george jr.'s brain. Warning! Graphic intensive. 
Wear galoshes and slap on the pithy helmet. 


<P>

<H2><A HREF="wh1.html">white house email</a></H2>

<!--text here-->
Instead of alerting you to <a href="http://www.msn.com">Microsoft Network's</a> plans to  launch new RIFF technology and live chat with <a href="http://www.msn.com"> Phillip Glass from Feb. 7-13</a>, <a href="http://www.msn.com">Jan Silberry from Feb. 14-20</a>, <a href="http://www.msn.com">Love Mongers from Feb. 21-27</a> and <a href="http://www.msn.com">Keith Emerson from Feb. 28-March 6</a>, we instead offer you a surly roundup of genuine dispatches to and from the White House that were sent during those glory years of Oliver North, Iran-Contra and the whole White House mess. That, my friends, is entertainment.


<P>
<IMG SRC="hose3.jpg" WIDTH=66 HEIGHT=128 hspace=10 ALIGN=right>
<H2><A HREF="grayson.html">panty hose wars</a></H2>

<!--text here-->
From underwear to underlings, has <b>george jr.</b> no limits? Frankly, no. In this dispatch from attorney Richard Grayson, we can see how the high courts continue to uphold our leggings, er, rights.

<br clear=all>
<p>

<H2><A HREF="baker.html">a poem</A></H2>
<!--text here-->
OK, your daughter may marry a restaurant, but would you want one moving in next door? David Baker offers  a tonic by way of a poem. 
<br clear=all>
<P>

<p>

</td>

<td valign=top>

<A HREF="index.html"><IMG SRC="home.gif" WIDTH=132 HEIGHT=36 border=0></A>
<br>
<br>
<a href="/feb97/features.html"><IMG SRC="/graphics/gotofb.gif" WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=34 BORDER=0></a>
<br>
