<title>george jr. / february 1997 / features / q & a / john edgar wideman </title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" LINK="#336699" VLINK="#c0c0c0" ALINK="#c0c0c0">
<a href="/feb97/features.html"><IMG SRC="/graphics/gotofb.gif" WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=34 BORDER=0 align=left></a>
