already gone to the press in Teguc.  15 dead, 30 wounded reported.
Recalls the Christmas Masacre of 81, the Christmas March with Bishop
Shafler of 83.  Those bastards.  Still no word from CIA if they've
confirmed.  Have a gut feeling it happened though.

