<A HREF="http://www.io.org/~toadaly/">Margaret Atwood</A>, http://www.io.org/~toadaly/ 
<P>
<A HREF="http://www.empirenet.com/~rdaeley/authors/amis.html">Martin Amis</A>, http://www.empirenet.com/~rdaeley/authors/amis.html
<P>
<A HREF="http://www.columbia.edu/acis/bartleby/bartlett">Bartlett's Familiar Quotations</A>, http://www.columbia.edu/acis/bartleby/bartlett 
