<H4>gallery:</H4>
<H3>michael Bowers portfolio</H3>
<blockquote>
  
   Traditional realist Michael Bowers originally is from a small town in Indiana, but has lived in  Columbus since 1968.  He has been active in the arts since 1980, and is a member of the Columbus Art League.<P>

  
     He studied portraiture with Marvin Triguba for three years, and attended Columbus College of Art and Design in the Fine Arts Department after graduating from  Indiana Universtiy and
       Ohio State University.<P>

The works:<P>
