<html><head><title>george jr. / january 1997 / faq / What george jr. is</title></head><body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" LINK="#336699" VLINK="#c0c0c0" ALINK="#c0c0c0"><a href="/december/departments.html"><IMG SRC="/graphics/gotofb.gif" WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=34 BORDER=0 align=left></a><A HREF="index.html"><IMG SRC="/graphics/home2.gif" WIDTH=132 HEIGHT=36 border=0 align=right></A><br clear=all><hr><br><H2>What george jr. is</H2><blockquote><p align=left><br><b>george jr.</b> is a monthly literary 'zine -- call it a boxcar, a kazoo, a magazine, whatever you like -- ever so devoted to literature, the national obsessions, fiction and news, sometimes, about the software and entertainment biz.<p><b>george jr.</b> consists of views, frequently an artist's portfolio, press releases and news, much of it sent to george jr.'s world headquarters via its faxline (614-899-9011), which usually george jr. remembers to leave turned on during the day before he heads to work.</blockquote><P><HR><BR><a href="/jan97/departments.html"><IMG SRC="/graphics/gotofb.gif" WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=34 BORDER=0 align=left></a><A HREF="index.html"><IMG SRC="../graphics/home2.gif" WIDTH=132 HEIGHT=36 border=0 align=right></A></BODY></HTML>
