<h2><a href="what.html">What george jr. is</a></h2>
Uncomplicated cafe download - rough and potent,
tarpaulin edged with lace.

<P>
<h2><a href="who.html">Who george jr. is</a></h2>
My zine makes my
mom stand back and say, "Hey, son, if I can't hold your 
magazine in my hands it just doesn't exist!"
<P>

<h2><a href="wants.html">What george jr. wants</a></h2>
Not to be confused with George Magazine, a calcium deposit, a misplaced 
modifier or the nation of Tanzania.

