Labor arbitrator Gerald M. Sutliff is mad as hell and doesn't want to take it anymore. (Good thing he hasn't met Humots, the demon book thief.) Now we ask you, is <i>Smoke and Mirrors</i> about law, or disorder?

<H2><A HREF="qabowen.html">q &#38; a</A></H2>

