<h2><A HREF="yang.html">belle yang q &#38; a</a></h2>

<!--text here-->
"Life is but a dream, a bubble, lightning, morning dew, ephemeral, changeable."

<P>
<h2><A HREF="crais.html">mystery novelist robert crais q &#38; a</a></h2>
<!--text here-->
"Like most people, I'm frustrated by all of this."

<P>
<h2><A HREF="halperin.html">sci-fi novelist james halperin q &#38; a</a></h2>

<!--text here-->
"I envision a world  creeping ever more steadily toward self-destruction, which can be averted only  by people willingly giving up some of their liberties -- a portion of their  right to privacy."

<P>

<h2><A HREF="future.html">everything's future</A></h2>

<!--text here-->

