<h2><a href="npr.html">national public rodeo</a></h2>
<!--text here-->
Art, music, tube, movie, Web and concert news of the world, updated by you with a click, at this month's newsstand for digerati.

<P>
<h2><A HREF="lex.html">the joy of lex</A></h2>

<!--text here-->
"Part of the process of revision," says Donald Hall, ''is to force you to think over every single word. So a form like that, which basically is a constraint, actually becomes a liberation, because it requires you to think every word through until every one is perfect."
  

<P>
<h2><A HREF="weights.html">weights & measures</A></h2>
<!--text here-->
We have measured the 12 signs, the four numbers, the three blocks, the two hearts and the one mind and come up, this month, with what is oh-so crucial to your well-being whilst you shovel snow.

<P>

