<h2>gallery</h2><h3>Laura Patterson</h3>
Laura Patterson¹s paintings and scenic design have been exhibited in Ohio and North Carolina, including the <I>Extending the Portrait</I> show of the Columbus Art League, as well as at the Roy G. Biv gallery, the Ohio Women¹s Caucus for Art and the Jonathan Bollas Gallery.
