<title>george jr. / august 1996 / faq / What george jr. is</title>

</head>

<body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" LINK="#2F4F2F" VLINK="#c0c0c0" ALINK="#c0c0c0">

<a href="../august/faq.html"><IMG SRC="../graphics/gotofaq.gif" WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=34 BORDER=0 align=left></a>

<A HREF="index.html"><IMG SRC="../graphics/home.gif" WIDTH=133 HEIGHT=34 border=0 align=right></A>

<br clear=all>

<hr>

<br>

<H2>What george jr. is</H2>
<blockquote>
<p align=left><br>

<b>george jr.</b> is a monthly literary 'zine -- call it a boxcar, a kazoo, a 
magazine, whatever you like -- ever so devoted to literature, the 
national obsessions, fiction, politics not as usual; and news about the 
software and entertainment biz.
<p>

<b>george jr.</b> consists of views, an artist's portfolio, press releases and 
news, much of it sent to george jr.'s world headquarters via its faxline 
(614-899-9011), which usually george jr. remembers to leave turned on 
during the day before he heads to work.
</blockquote>

<P>

<HR><BR>

<a href="../august/faq.html"><IMG SRC="../graphics/gotofaq.gif" WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=34 BORDER=0 align=left></a>

<A HREF="index.html"><IMG SRC="../graphics/home.gif" WIDTH=133 HEIGHT=34 border=0 align=right></A>
