From <i>The Way We Are, </i>Copyright 1994 by Margaret Visser; Published in the United States in 1996 by Faber and Faber Inc., which kindly gave <b>george jr.</b> the rights to reprint this essay.  The book is available for ordering at all independent and chain bookstores, or call CUP Services at 1-800-666-2211.
</BLOCKQUOTE></BLOCKQUOTE>
