<H2>What george jr. is</H2>
<blockquote>
<p align=left><br>

<b>george jr.</b> is a monthly literary 'zine -- call it a boxcar, a kazoo, a 
magazine, whatever you like -- ever so devoted to literature, the 
national obsessions, fiction and news about the 
software and entertainment biz.
<p>

<b>george jr.</b> consists of views, an artist's portfolio, press releases and 
news, much of it sent to george jr.'s world headquarters via its faxline 
(614-899-9011), which usually george jr. remembers to leave turned on 
during the day before he heads to work.
</blockquote>

<P>

