<title>george jr. / october 1996 / faq / Who george jr. is</title>

</head>

<body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" LINK="#2F4F2F" VLINK="#c0c0c0" ALINK="#c0c0c0">

<a href="/october/features.html"><IMG SRC="/graphics/gotof.gif" WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=34 BORDER=0 align=left></a>

