<br clear=all>


<hr>

<br>

<H2>What george jr. wants</H2>
<blockquote>
<p align=left><br>


Editorial copy from you, for which we can pay neither a shilling nor a pence. <b>george jr.</b> is especially interested in Interesting Info smartly conveyed, and also original essays, short-short fiction and even reprints (which we secure permission to reprint, always, and for which we neither pay nor charge a dime). 
<p>
<b>george jr. </b>doesn't own a scanner so kindly send your art digitized or as a print (if you must, but never as slides). Send letters as email, and press releases as faxes.  If you'd like to send 3-D objects for review, send them to george jr., Box 2962, Columbus, Ohio 43216-2962 (US of A).
<p>
Now, on with the show.
</blockquote>

<P>

