<title>george jr. / december 1996 / arcadia /jerry roscoe poems</title>

</head>

<body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" LINK="#2F4F2F" VLINK="#c0c0c0" 
ALINK="#c0c0c0">

<a href="/december/arcadia.html"><IMG SRC="/graphics/gotoa.gif" WIDTH=150 
