.lib.utexas.edu/Libs/HRC/HRHRC/">Harry Ransom Humanities Research Center</a><br>Superlative archives at the University of Texas at Austin.<br><IMG SRC="point.gif" WIDTH="18" HEIGHT="13" BORDER=0ALIGN="LEFT"NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" BORDER="0" ISMAP><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.shakespeare.com/">Shakespeare Web </A><br>    Act I on the bard's life and works, plus information about festivals.</A><br><IMG SRC="point.gif" WIDTH="18" HEIGHT="13" BORDER=0ALIGN="LEFT"NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" BORDER="0" ISMAP><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.yasuda-u.ac.jp/LitCalendar.html">Literary Hyper-Calendar</A><br>    Literature day by day, month by month.<BR><IMG SRC="point.gif" WIDTH="18" HEIGHT="13" BORDER=0ALIGN="LEFT"NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" BORDER="0" ISMAP><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.cs.cmu.edu/Web/People/spok/banned-books.html/">Banned Books Online   </A><br>A list of problematic texts and why.<BR><IMG SRC="point.gif" WIDTH="18" HEIGHT="13" BORDER=0ALIGN="LEFT"NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" BORDER="0" ISMAP><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.amazon.com/">Amazon.com Books</A><br> Huge bookstore with interesting non-commercial links.<BR><!-- Horizontal Line Tag --><HR><CENTER><H3><B>Five search engines</B></H3><A HREF="http://www.yahoo.com/">Yahoo!</A> //<A HREF="http://www.lycos.com/">Lycos</A> //<A HREF="http://www.mckinley.com/">Magellan  </A> //<A HREF="http:// www.excite.com/">Excite</A> //<A HREF="http:// www.altavista.com/">Alta Vista</A> </CENTER><br><!-- Horizontal Line Tag --><HR>    <B><CENTER><H3>Not quite five offline browsers</H3></CENTER></B><A HREF="http://www.pointcast.com/">PointCast Network</A> //<A HREF="http://www.tenmax.com/index.html/">Teleport Pro </A> //<A HREF="http://www.firstfloor.com/">Smart Bookmarks</A> //<A HREF="http:// www.ffg.com/">WebWhacker</A><br></blockquote></BLOCKQUOTE><p><HR><BR><a href="/december/departments.html"><IMG SRC="/graphics/gotod.gif" WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=34 BORDER=0 align=l