ic Records, Los Angeles: 310-449-2100<br>Epic Records, New York: 212-833-8000<br>ESPN Radio Network: 22-456-5688<br>Esquire Magazine: 212-459-7500<br>Forbes: 800-888-9896<br>Foreign Policy: 800-678-0916<br>Fortune: 800-621-8000<br>Geffen Records, Los Angeles: 310-278-9010<br>Geffen Records, New York: 212-841-8600<br>The Globe: 310-207-7800<br>Hits Magazine: 818-501-7900<br>Hollywood Records: 818-560-5670<br>Life Magazine: 212-522-1212<br>Microsystems: 908-302-3865<br>MGM/UA: 310-280-6000<br>Movie Posters and Photos: 204-783-3717<br>MTV Networks: 212-258-8000<br>MTV News: 212-258-8826<br>National Book Critics Circle: 215-854-5615<br>New Line Cinema: 818-995-6049<br>The New Republic: 800-827-1289<br>The New Press: 212-629-8812 <br>PR Newswire: 800-832-5522<br>Paramount Pictures: 213-956-5000<br>People Magazine: 212-522-1212<br>Reprise Records: 818-846-9090<br>Spin Magazine: 212-633-8200<br>Sports Illustrated: 212-522-1212<br>Tri-Star Pictures: 310-280-7700<br>USA Today: 703-276-3400<br>Variety: 213-857-6600<br>Warner Brothers Pictures: 818-954-6000<br>Warner-Electra-Asylum: 212-275-4700</blockquote></blockquote><P><HR><BR><a href="/december/departments.html"><IMG SRC="/graphics/gotod.gif" WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=34 BORDER=0 align=left></a><A HREF="index.html"><IMG SRC="/graphics/home.gif" WIDTH=133 HEIGHT=34 border=0 align=right></A></BODY></HTML>
