<html><head><title>george jr. / december 1996 / faq / What george jr. wants</title></head><body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" LINK="#2F4F2F" VLINK="#c0c0c0" ALINK="#c0c0c0"><a href="/december/departments.html"><IMG SRC="/graphics/gotof.gif" WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=34 BORDER=0 align=left></a><A HREF="index.html"><IMG SRC="/graphics/home.gif" WIDTH=133 HEIGHT=34 border=0 align=right></A><br clear=all><hr><br><H2>What george jr. wants</H2><blockquote><p align=left><br>Editorial copy from you, for which we can pay neither a shilling nor a pence. <b>george jr.</b> is especially interested in Interesting Info smartly conveyed, and also original essays, short-short fiction and even reprints (which we secure permission to reprint, always, and for which we neither pay nor charge a dime). Especially coveted: columns on music and film.<p><b>george jr. </b>doesn't own a scanner so kindly send your art digitized or as a print (if you must, but never as slides). Send letters as email, and press releases as faxes.  If you'd like to send 3-D objects for review, send them to george jr., Box 2962, Columbus, Ohio 43216-2962 (US of A).<p>Now, on with the show.</blockquote><P><HR><BR><a href="/december/departments.html"><IMG SRC="/graphics/gotof.gif" WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=34 BORDER=0 align=left></a><A HREF="index.html"><IMG SRC="../graphics/home.gif" WIDTH=133 HEIGHT=34 border=0 align=right></A></BODY></HTML>
