<H4><b>Welcome to TCCM Design's 
Homepage.</b></h4><p> As a Web Page Design and Resource Center, TCCM Design is
dedicated to helping you put your business on the Internet 
where it can be reached by thousands of potential customers 24-hours per 
day, seven days a week. Linking your business to the world is our 
only business.<p><img
src="gl07st_a.gif"><p> We design custom web pages for 
business clients. To see a list of our clients follow this <a 
href="http://www.tccmweb.com/biz.html">link</a> or click on 
the Business District section below. We also offer on-site consultation, 
instruction, and even installation.</H4> 
<P><IMG SRC="images/line.gif"><P>If you've got a project in mind and would 
like an estimate, feel free to fill out our on-line<a 
href="form.html"> information request</a> or <a 
href="mailto:swcm@sprynet.com"><img src="images/amailbox.gif">email</a> 
us.<p>
<EM>(Please note: Our pages are optimized for HTML 3.0 standards along 
with Microsoft Internet Explorer and Netscape's enhanced tags)</EM><P>
