<h2 align="center">Tourism and Travel Related Links</h2>

<p align="center"><img src="images/rainban.gif" align="bottom" >

<p align="center">Though it's a small list now, rest assured it will grow!!
<a href="http://www.roundthebend.com/">
<p align="center">'Round The Bend</a> A cool  resource for upstate travel.
<a href="http://www.infovantage.com/ny/saratoga/">
