src="images/rainban.gif"><br><H1>Sidelines 
and Diversions</H1><H3>Internet Interests and
Oddities</H3><P>Looking for something to do? Hit these sites and
watch
boredom melt away. There's no general order to them, just a lot
of links 
for those of you with a little free time!</P><img
src="images/line.gif"><BR>
<img src="images/bell.gif"><a href="santa.html"> TCCM'S HOLIDAY SITE</a> 
with links to 
hundreds of great Christmas and holiday related sites around the web<p>
<A 
HREF="http://kzsu.stanford.edu/uwi/br/off-world.html"
>The Bladerunner Homepage</A><BR><P></P><A
HREF="http://www.ee.pdx.edu/~caseyh/horror/horror.html"
>The Cabinet of Dr. Casey </A>(Horror film archive)<P>
<a href="http://www.cs.rochester.edu/u/ferguson/schedules">Sports
Schedules as You Like 'em</a><p>
<a href="http://www.nets.com/earwaves">Earwaves Radio
Network</a><p><a
href="http://www.acns.nwu.edu/jazz/lists/clubs.html">Jazz Clubs
Around the World</a><p>
<a href="http://sunsite.unc.edu/Dave/drfun.html">Doctor Fun</a>
 Doctor Fun is a cartoon that's been running on the Internet
since 1993.<p><a href="http://www.unitedmedia.com">United
Media</a> Peanuts comic strip info.<p>
<a href="http://www.riddler.com">Riddler</a> Riddler is the
entertainment network giving you the opportunity to win cash and
prizes.<p>
<a 
href="http://kuhttp.cc.ukans.edu/cwis/organizations/kucia/uroulette/uroulette.html">URouLette</a> Surf the Net.  Spin the wheel
of fortune and you are randomly directed to a different home<p>
<a href="http://www.mca.com">Cyberwalk</a> Sample the latest
products and entertainment from MCA/Universal.<p>
<a href="http://www.sony.com">Sony</a> Information on music,
pictures, electronics and interactive technology<p>
<a href="http://www.starwave.com">Starwave</a> Online News,
Entertainment, Sports and Tickets<p>
<a href="http://postcards.www.media.mit.edu/Postcards">The
Electric Postcard</a> Choose from a wide variety of electronic
postcards and e-mail to your friends and relatives.<p>
<a href="http://sunsite.unc.edu/btbin/birthday">World Birthday
Web</a> Receive personal birthday wishes from private individuals
over E-mail.<p><a href="http://www.cm.cf.ac.uk/Movies">Internet
Movie Database</a> Database of movies and movie topics created by
Internet users.<p><center><img src="images/ad.gif"><br><a 
href="mailto:tccm@tccmweb.com">Email us for ad rates</a></center><p><a 
href="http://voyager.paramount.com">Paramount Pictures</a> Online
Studio.   Interactive sites, get the latest studio news.<p> 
<a href="http://www.iuma.com">Internet Underground Music
Archive</a> Underground labels, bands, publications and news.<p>
<a href="http://www.eeb.ele.tue.nl/midi/index.html">MIDI</a>
Musical Instrument Digital Interface.  What is it?  Tools and
resources, FAQs and much more.<p><a href="http://metaverse.com">
Metaverse Internet Entertainment Network</a> News and features on
today's music.<p>
<a href="http://www.music.indiana.edu/misc/music_resources.html">
Music Resources on the Internet</a> A fantastic collection of
music sources, academic sites, general information and more.<p>
<a href="http://www.stones.com">Rolling Stones</a> Official Stone
site. Cool pages, pictures, sound samples and interviews.<p>
<a href="http://american.recordings.com/wwwofmusic/ubl.html"> The
Ultimate Band List</a> Browse the web's largest interactive list
of music links.<p>
<a href="http://www.timeinc.com/vibe/mmm/music.html">VIBE
on-line</a> Great site for unique local geographic area 
information, specific artists and labels, reviews for all styles
of music.<p><a
href="http://american.recordings.com/wwwofmusic/index.html">
World Wide Web of Music</a> Great source for Hotspots, coolest
radio stations, record stores, recording labels and a listing of
the ultimate bands.<p>
<a href="http://www.gorp.com">http://www.gorp.com</a> Great
Outdoor Recreation Pages Comprehensive list of activities, gear,
locations, attractions, trips and more for the outdoor
enthusiast.<p><a href="http://www.pbs.org">Public Broadcasting
System</a> On-line guide to the PBS. Includes:  what's on PBS,
Inside PBS, products, member stations and on-line newshour.<p>
<a href="http://ai.eecs.umich.edu/people/kennyp/sounds.html">
Sound Bites</a> Listen to TV show themes.  Complete list of shows
from the 50's to the 90's in alphabetical order.<p>
<a href="http://www.ugcs.caltech.edu/~werdna/sttng">Star Trek:
The Next Generation</a> Great information on Star Trek TNG
including episodes, cast and trivia.<p>
<a href="http://www.rutgers.edu/x-files.html">The X-Files</a>
Devoted to the Fox Television show "The X-Files".<p>
