<DOCHDR>
http://www.tccmweb.com:80/swcm/nov96/xmasgame.htm 207.78.230.89 19970216203300 text/html 34265
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 16 Feb 1997 20:34:06 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 34093
Last-modified: Mon, 25 Nov 1996 22:13:55 GMT
